<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīcembukalla bhaṭṭara<unclear>ka</unclear> śrīraṇasāgarāḷupēndrarā
<lb n="2"/>rājyaduḷḷe kavuḷappaḷmuḻteṟiye padineṇṭu paṭṭaṇamum
<lb n="3"/>nitta vyavaste paḍi meḷasu Akkiyuḷḷa nelluḷḷamudi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>yapurada nagaramondu pēṟingoṟu goḷivaḷḷadōrvva<unclear>ḷḷa nā</unclear>ge koḷvadu
<lb n="5"/>Ī vyavasthe Āge Ūru rakṣippadu Idāndēvarggallade peṟarkkoḷvoroḷarā
<lb n="6"/>śivaḷḷiya brabmapuramu maḻida mahāpāta<note n="144-2">The letterta is written below the line.</note>kanakku Avīcimahanarakakke
<lb n="7"/>bhāgyanakkum <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied><note n="144-3">At the bottom is carved the figure of the <hi rend="italic">tris11ūla.</hi></note>
</p>

